<episodedetails><title>The Deal: Trump, Bukele, &amp; The Gangs of El Salvador</title><plot>The Salvadoran president’s deal with Trump to imprison deportees, and what each stood to gain. With the Salvadoran news outlet El Faro, now reporting from exile, President Nayib Bukele’s tangled history with the gangs the U.S. says it is fighting.</plot></episodedetails>